<HEADLINE>  Dollar Hits 3-Year Low Against Yen </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- The dollar plumbed a 3 1/2-year low against the  
Japanese yen for the second day in a row Wednesday as traders sold 
dollars in a continued reaction to strong U.S. trade deficit 
numbers. 
</P>
<P>
