Redskins touchdowns. 
</P>
<P>
	Gailey admitted he goofed on his play calling.  
</P>
<P>
	``After going back and watching the film, I'd probably change  
that and run the ball a little more in the third quarter,'' he 
said. ``At the time, I thought we were doing the right thing.'' 
</P>
<P>
	After Dallas returned to the ground game, Smith and backup Chris  
Warren moved the chains and kept the Washington defense from laying 
