a 21-point comeback that matched the biggest in franchise history. 
</P>
<P>
	``Chan is the head coach and he got it under control,'' Smith  
said. ``We got the running game going and things went back to 
clicking like they were in the first quarter. 
</P>
<P>
	``So it all worked out.''  
  	   	
</P>
