</P>
<P>
	``If you want to ask football questions at this point, you're  
probably better off,'' he said. ``You'll get an answer.'' 
</P>
<P>
	While McNown admits the case is ``a distraction,'' Jauron said  
he hasn't shown it. 
</P>
<P>
	``In the general terms that we've ever spoken about it, he  
understands there's clearly something wrong with the general issue 
and the specifics of it,'' Jauron said. ``He's focused, and 
hopefully this will get cleared up real soon.'' 
  	   	
</P>
